window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The dragons have been freed, and now the stage is set for the final battle with the horrors.</b></p> <p>Nico will have to grow stronger and grow his kingdom of dragons if they are going to stand against what is coming.</p> <p>Ileria is theirs, but only the rise of a new dragon emperor will be enough to keep it intact.</p> <p>Nico must seek the Horned Crown.</p>"; 
